casebody.data:
The IRWIN LAW FIRM, P.A., Plaintiff-Petitioner,
v.
Richard GRABOWSKY, Defendant-Respondent. C-173 September Term 2017
079513 Supreme Court of New Jersey. October 16, 2017

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004800-13 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
